的目的地！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/hequhecong/featured.png"/></item><item><title>感觉马上就要离开了</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/feeling-soon-left-the/</link><pubDate>Mon, 03 Nov 2008 22:56:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/feeling-soon-left-the/</guid><description>班会提到实习安排，突然意识到毕业临近，却莫名从容。或许因心态豁达，对得失看得轻，便选择淡然离开。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/feeling-soon-left-the/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>